<instructions>For each entry in the input, extract tokens and assign the appropriate NER tag based on the context of the token. Ensure that the output is a list of strings formatted as specified, with each token and its tag clearly identified.</instructions>

Name: desired_output, dtype: object`</examples>
<context>Input data is raw tokenized text, and the desired output consists of tokens with their Named Entity Recognition label. <user>Transform the given input data into the desired NER labeled format.</user></system>
